to\": 927}, {\"ngram\": \"mistakes\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 940}, {\"ngram\": \"routines\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 956}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having officiated at the Commonwealth, Asian and SEA Games, he made his Olympic debut in Paris and noted that the pressure is not unlike what the athletes face.\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 1118, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 983, \"end\": 995, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999987298906, \"rank\": 1.2697758409809618e-09, \"text\": \"Commonwealth\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 997, \"end\": 1002, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.482636609816919e-20, \"text\": \"Asian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 1007, \"end\": 1016, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southeast_Asian_Games\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6458752197054188e-16, \"text\": \"SEA Games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southeast_Asian_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southeast_Asian_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 1047, \"end\": 1052, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.071747747091236e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his Olympic debut\", \"from\": 1026, \"to\": 1043}, {\"ngram\": \"the pressure\", \"from\": 1068, \"to\": 1080}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 1100, \"to\": 1112}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He told The Sunday Times: \\\"We get to judge all the star gymnasts from all over the world.\", \"from\": 1120, \"to\": 1209, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1132, \"end\": 1144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Straits_Times\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.2538255360515056e-21, \"text\": \"Sunday Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Straits_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Straits_Times\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the star gymnasts\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1184}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1199, \"to\": 1208}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am the only judge from South-east Asia, I would not want to make any mistakes in such a prestigious event and tarnish the reputation of Asian judges.\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1363, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1350, \"end\": 1355, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.482636609816919e-20, \"text\": \"Asian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the only judge\", \"from\": 1217, \"to\": 1231}, {\"ngram\": \"South-east Asia\", \"from\": 1237, \"to\": 1252}, {\"ngram\": \"any mistakes\", \"from\": 1279, \"to\": 1291}, {\"ngram\": \"such a prestigious event\", \"from\": 1295, \"to\": 1319}, {\"ngram\": \"the reputation\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1346}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Hence, the pressure I have felt is tremendous, and I have never been so stressed out before.\\\"\", \"from\": 1365, \"to\": 1459, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pressure\", \"from\": 1373, \"to\": 1385}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The former national gymnast decided to go for a judging exam after setting up a gymnastics academy.\", \"from\": 1461, \"to\": 1560, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The former national gymnast\", \"from\": 1461, \"to\": 1488}, {\"ngram\": \"a judging exam\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1521}, {\"ngram\": \"a gymnastics academy\", \"from\": 1539, \"to\": 1559}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He failed the exam initially before passing in 2006.\", \"from\": 1561, \"to\": 1613, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the exam\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1579}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sng quipped: \\\"As gymnasts, judges were the ones we used to blame for our low scores.\", \"from\": 1615, \"to\": 1699, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sng\", \"from\": 1615, \"to\": 1618}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnasts\", \"from\": 1632, \"to\": 1640}, {\"ngram\": \"judges\", \"from\": 1642, \"to\": 1648}, {\"ngram\": \"the ones\", \"from\": 1654, \"to\": 1662}, {\"ngram\": \"our low scores\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1698}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My first judging experience was at a local club competition and I got a complaint from parents for awarding very low scores.\\\"\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1825, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My first judging experience\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1727}, {\"ngram\": \"a local club competition\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1759}, {\"ngram\": \"a complaint\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 1781}, {\"ngram\": \"parents\", \"from\": 1787, \"to\": 1794}, {\"ngram\": \"very low scores\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 1823}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here in Paris, he also worries about his own elimination as he has seen judges sidelined from the competition.\", \"from\": 1827, \"to\": 1937, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1835, \"end\": 1840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.071747747091236e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his own elimination\", \"from\": 1864, \"to\": 1883}, {\"ngram\": \"judges\", \"from\": 1899, \"to\": 1905}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 1921, \"to\": 1936}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is why he studiously goes through past championship videos to practise his scoring.\", \"from\": 1938, \"to\": 2026, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"past championship videos\", \"from\": 1977, \"to\": 2001}, {\"ngram\": \"his scoring\", \"from\": 2014, \"to\": 2025}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Singaporean William Lee is a diving judge officiating at his third Olympics.\", \"from\": 2028, \"to\": 2104, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2028, \"end\": 2039, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singaporeans\", \"score\": 0.9930989996932044, \"rank\": 0.006948955047546781, \"text\": \"Singaporean\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singaporeans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singaporeans\"}, {\"begin\": 2040, \"end\": 2051, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_C._Lee\", \"score\": 0.9991309813341742, \"rank\": 0.0008697716297208092, \"text\": \"William Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_C._Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_C._Lee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a diving judge\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2069}, {\"ngram\": \"his third Olympics\", \"from\": 2085, \"to\": 2103}]}, {\"sentence\": \"PHOTO: COURTESY OF WILLIAM LEE It is the same for diving judge William Lee, who still \\\"feels butterflies in my stomach\\\" despite this being his third time officiating at the Olympics after Rio 2016 and Tokyo 2020.\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2319, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2125, \"end\": 2136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_C._Lee\", \"score\": 0.9991309813341742, \"rank\": 0.0008697716297208092, \"text\": \"WILLIAM LEE\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_C._Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_C._Lee\"}, {\"begin\": 2170, \"end\": 2181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_C._Lee\", \"score\": 0.9991309813341742, \"rank\": 0.0008697716297208092, \"text\": \"William Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088