tence\": \"He said: \\\"Some of these divers make extremely difficult and powerful dives look graceful and beautiful.\", \"from\": 3157, \"to\": 3260, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these divers\", \"from\": 3175, \"to\": 3187}, {\"ngram\": \"extremely difficult and powerful dives\", \"from\": 3193, \"to\": 3231}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And when they have a perfect entry into the water, they \\\"disappear\\\" without any ripples.\", \"from\": 3261, \"to\": 3349, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a perfect entry\", \"from\": 3280, \"to\": 3295}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 3301, \"to\": 3310}, {\"ngram\": \"any ripples\", \"from\": 3337, \"to\": 3348}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Called a 'rip dive', the impact on the diver's entry also sends a shockwave that hits us poolside.\", \"from\": 3351, \"to\": 3450, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a 'rip dive\", \"from\": 3359, \"to\": 3370}, {\"ngram\": \"the impact\", \"from\": 3373, \"to\": 3383}, {\"ngram\": \"the diver's entry\", \"from\": 3387, \"to\": 3404}, {\"ngram\": \"a shockwave\", \"from\": 3416, \"to\": 3427}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3438, \"to\": 3440}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is a truly phenomenal experience.\", \"from\": 3451, \"to\": 3487, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a truly phenomenal experience\", \"from\": 3457, \"to\": 3486}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sharing his own challenges, he said:\\\"Each dive takes only a few seconds, and we must enter our scores into the keypad within two seconds of the diver entering the water.\", \"from\": 3489, \"to\": 3658, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his own challenges\", \"from\": 3497, \"to\": 3515}, {\"ngram\": \"said:\\\"Each\", \"from\": 3520, \"to\": 3530}, {\"ngram\": \"dive\", \"from\": 3531, \"to\": 3535}, {\"ngram\": \"only a few seconds\", \"from\": 3542, \"to\": 3560}, {\"ngram\": \"our scores\", \"from\": 3580, \"to\": 3590}, {\"ngram\": \"the keypad\", \"from\": 3596, \"to\": 3606}, {\"ngram\": \"two seconds\", \"from\": 3614, \"to\": 3625}, {\"ngram\": \"the diver\", \"from\": 3629, \"to\": 3638}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 3648, \"to\": 3657}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When we sit on the judging chair, it can be from one to three hours, depending on the number of competitors.\", \"from\": 3659, \"to\": 3767, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the judging chair\", \"from\": 3674, \"to\": 3691}, {\"ngram\": \"one to three hours\", \"from\": 3708, \"to\": 3726}, {\"ngram\": \"the number\", \"from\": 3741, \"to\": 3751}, {\"ngram\": \"competitors\", \"from\": 3755, \"to\": 3766}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So it requires a lot of concentration over long periods.\", \"from\": 3769, \"to\": 3826, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3785, \"to\": 3790}, {\"ngram\": \"concentration\", \"from\": 3794, \"to\": 3807}, {\"ngram\": \"long periods\", \"from\": 3813, \"to\": 3825}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We also do not get the benefit of video replays and we cannot confer with other judges before we give our scores.\\\"\", \"from\": 3827, \"to\": 3941, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the benefit\", \"from\": 3846, \"to\": 3857}, {\"ngram\": \"video replays\", \"from\": 3861, \"to\": 3874}, {\"ngram\": \"other judges\", \"from\": 3901, \"to\": 3913}, {\"ngram\": \"our scores\", \"from\": 3929, \"to\": 3939}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Former national hockey player Lim Hong Zhen officiating at the 2024 Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 3943, \"to\": 4026, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3973, \"end\": 3981, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limahong\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lim Hong\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limahong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limahong\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 4002, \"to\": 4025}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 39-year-old was an umpire at the Paris Olympics, the third Games he has officiated at.\", \"from\": 4027, \"to\": 4117, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an umpire\", \"from\": 4047, \"to\": 4056}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 4060, \"to\": 4078}]}, {\"sentence\": \"PHOTO: YAN HUCKENDUBLER Hockey umpire Lim Hong Zhen takes his preparation to another level, as he went on a 10-month fitness programme that included runs and high-intensity interval training for three days a week.\", \"from\": 4119, \"to\": 4333, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4126, \"end\": 4129, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Esteban_Yan\", \"score\": 0.9999999683022912, \"rank\": 3.169770700348246e-08, \"text\": \"YAN\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Esteban_Yan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Esteban_Yan\"}, {\"begin\": 4158, \"end\": 4166, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limahong\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lim Hong\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limahong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limahong\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"PHOTO\", \"from\": 4119, \"to\": 4124}, {\"ngram\": \"his preparation\", \"from\": 4177, \"to\": 4192}, {\"ngram\": \"another level\", \"from\": 4196, \"to\": 4209}, {\"ngram\": \"a 10-month fitness programme\", \"from\": 4225, \"to\": 4253}, {\"ngram\": \"runs\", \"from\": 4268, \"to\": 4272}, {\"ngram\": \"high-intensity interval training\", \"from\": 4277, \"to\": 4309}, {\"ngram\": \"three days\", \"from\": 4314, \"to\": 4324}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He also officiates matches on weekends.\", \"from\": 4334, \"to\": 4373, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"matches\", \"from\": 4353, \"to\": 4360}, {\"ngram\": \"weekends\", \"from\": 4364, \"to\": 4372}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The former national player, who started international umpiring in 2007 and has been to all the major Games, takes it very seriously as officiating at the Olympics is \\\"the pinnacle of a field hockey technical official's career\\\".\", \"from\": 4375, \"to\": 4602, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The former national player\", \"from\": 4375, \"to\": 4401}, {\"ngram\": \"international umpiring\", \"from\": 4415, \"to\": 4437}, {\"ngram\": \"all the major Games\", \"from\": 4462, \"to\": 4481}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4525, \"to\": 4537}, {\"ngram\": \"the pinnacle\", \"from\": 4542, \"to\": 4554}, {\"ngram\": \"a field hockey technical official's career\", \"from\": 4558, \"to\": 4600}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Likening each match to a \\\"mini final\\\", the 39-year-old said: \\\"Teams will play their hearts out and we officials must be ready from the first whistle to be on top of our game.\", \"from\": 4604, \"to\": 4778, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"each match\", \"from\": 4613, \"to\": 4623}, {\"ngram\": \"Teams\", \"from\": 4666, \"to\": 4671}, {\"ngram\": \"their hearts\", \"from\": 4682, \"to\": 4694}, {\"ngram\": \"we officials\", \"from\": 4703, \"to\": 4715}, {\"ngram\": \"the first whistle\", \"from\": 4735, \"to\": 4752}, {\"ngram\": \"top\", \"from\": 4762, \"to\": 4765}, {\"ngram\": \"our game\", \"from\": 4769, \"to\": 4777}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is a true showcase of our capabilities, dedication and hard work we put in, and we are able to let the world see how Singapore can produce top hockey officials.\\\"\", \"from\": 4779, \"to\": 4945, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4901, \"end\": 4910, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.441735137283872e-19, \"text\": \"Singapore\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a true showcase\", \"from\": 4787, \"to\": 4802}, {\"ngram\": \"our capabilities\", \"from\": 4806, \"to\": 4822}, {\"ngram\": \"dedication\", \"from\": 4824, \"to\": 4834}, {\"ngram\": \"hard work\", \"from\": 4839, \"to\": 4848}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 4883, \"to\": 4892}, {\"ngram\": \"top hockey officials\", \"from\": 4923, \"to\": 4943}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Off the field of play, Tessa Cho leads various administrative functions - such as accreditation, accommodation, transport, hospitality and ticketing - to ensure a smooth and enjoyable Games experience for all at the table tennis venue.\", \"from\": 4947, \"to\": 5182, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4976, \"end\": 4979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Cho\", \"score\": 0.9999999914853106, \"rank\": 8.336323679034586e-09, \"text\": \"Cho\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Cho\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Cho\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 4951, \"to\": 4960}, {\"ngram\": \"play\", \"from\": 4964, \"to\": 4968}, {\"ngram\": \"various administrative functions\", \"from\": 4986, \"to\": 5018}, {\"ngram\": \"accreditation\", \"from\": 5029, \"to\": 5042}, {\"ngram\": \"accommodation\", \"from\": 5044, \"to\": 5057}, {\"ngram\": \"transport\", \"from\": 5059, \"to\": 5068}, {\"ngram\": \"hospitality\", \"from\": 5070, \"to\": 5081}, {\"ngram\": \"ticketing\", \"from\": 5086, \"to\": 5095}, {\"ngram\": \"a smooth and enjoyable Games experience\", \"from\": 5108, \"to\": 5147}, {\"ngram\": \"the table tennis venue\", \"from\": 5159, \"to\": 5181}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 30-year-old, who has travelled the world to observe how different sporting events are hosted in 2024, noted that even at the Olympics, there is now \\\"a lot more emphasis on the entertainment and show presentation aspect\\\".\", \"from\": 5184, \"to\": 5408, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 5219, \"to\": 5228}, {\"ngram\": \"how different sporting events\", \"from\": 5240, \"to\": 5269}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 5309, \"to\": 5321}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot more emphasis\", \"from\": 5337, \"to\": 5356}, {\"ngram\": \"the entertainment and show presentation aspect\", \"from\": 5360, \"to\": 5406}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Tokyo 2020 was highly restrictive due to the Covid-19 pandemic, while Paris 2024 has been very special with high spirits from both the locals and foreigners travelling here, she added.\", \"from\": 5410, \"to\": 5595, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tokyo\", \"from\": 5411, \"to\": 5416}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 5481, \"to\": 5486}, {\"ngram\": \"high spirits\", \"from\": 5519, \"to\": 5531}, {\"ngram\": \"both the locals\", \"from\": 5537, \"to\": 5552}, {\"ngram\": \"foreigners\", \"from\": 5557, \"to\": 5567}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her compatriots from the International Table Tennis Federation and World Table Tennis that are also supporting in various capacities at these Olympics are Charlotte Lourdes, Chern Mo Yi, Natiyaah Sakthimogan and Joel Chan.\", \"from\": 5597, \"to\": 5819, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5622, \"end\": 5659, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Table_Tennis_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Table Tennis Federation\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Table_Tennis_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Table_Tennis_Federation\"}, {\"begin\": 5752, \"end\": 5761, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Motor_Speedway\", \"score\": 0.9999962582034615, \"rank\": 3.739131525570245e-06, \"text\": \"Charlotte\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Motor_Speedway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Motor_Speedway\"}, {\"begin\": 5762, \"end\": 5769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lourdes\", \"score\": 0.999999